===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# A tough material produced from the [[skin]] of [[animal]]s, by [[tan]]ning or similar process, used e.g. for [[clothing]].
# A piece of the above used for [[polish]]ing.
# {{context|colloquial|lang=en}} A [[cricket]] ball or [[football]].
# (''plural'': '''leathers''') clothing made from the skin of animals, often worn by [[motorcycle]] riders.
# {{context|baseball|lang=en}} A good defensive play
#: ''Jones showed good '''leather''' to snare that [[liner]].''
# {{context|dated|humorous|lang=en}} The [[skin]].

